@node main "VCC"

     Name         : VCC

     Aliases      : VccOfTNC

     Type/Size    : Boot/1024

     Clones       : No Clones 

     Symptoms     : No Symptoms

     Discovered   : 20-06-93

     Way to infect: No infection

     Rating       : Dangerous

     Kickstarts   : 1.2/1.3/2.0

     Damage       : Overwrites boot+Rootblock.

     Manifestation: A graphic-screen appears

     Removal      : Install boot.

     Comments     : If  you`re  booting  with  an infected disk, the virus
                    shows the following graphic-screen:


                    Click on this gadget to see a @{" Demo " SYSTEM V-IFF:VCC} of the VCC virus.
                    Push left mouse button to return.


                    But  before  you will see  this  screen the virus will
                    overwrite  your Root and Bootblock when a special byte
                    is located in the BFEC01-register.



                    If you have such a destroyed disk, try Disksalv 2
                    to recover some files.
  
A.D 04-94
